
Q>	What's an article parent?
A>	Parents allow you to group your articles under different headings, this makes it easier for your visitors to find what they're looking for.

Q>	Can I create an article with more than one page?
A>	Yes. Enter your article as normal but seperate the pages by entering [newpage], this will seperate your article into pages with links to each page at the foot of each page.

Q>	What are the email / print icons for?
A>	These allow you to add a link at the end of your article to the 'email to a friend' and 'printer-friendly' pages.
